<lb ed="X" n="0793c06"/><lb ed="R059" n="0337b03"/><p xml:id="pX37p0793c0601" rend="margin-left:1em">卍云。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0793002" n="0793002"/>四十二章經略解。遺教經解。及<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0793003" n="0793003"/>七大人覺經
<lb ed="X" n="0793c07"/><lb ed="R059" n="0337b04"/>解之三般。合稱三經解。既分出別處。故省于此。</p></cb:div>
